ModÃ©lisation des effets; glmer

fit_1 = glmer(
  Presence ~ Turbidite + Prof_Moyenne + (1|Annee) + (1|Secteur),
            data = df,
            family = binomial)

fit_1_interaction = glmer(
  Presence ~ Turbidite * Prof_Moyenne + (1|Annee) + (1|Secteur),
            data = df,
            family = binomial)

compare_performance(fit_1, fit_1_interaction)
